com.mendeley.api.network

Class NullRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mendeley.api.network.NullRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RequestHandle

    public class NullRequest
extends java.lang.Object
implements RequestHandle
    A placeholder for a RequestHandle. The main purpose of this is to provide a valid handle for requests which have already failed prior to the generation of the RequestHandle. It is safe to call cancel on these.
